          "You remember your neonatehood as being idyllic, as your caring sire gently brought you into the world of vampires. You functioned fairly well for awhile, until your first encounter with the Sabbat. Now they've caught your scent, and you have had to constantly flee from the pack chasing you. They are terrible enemies and wish to feast on your heartsblood. You have spent the past 150 years on the move, traveling from city to city in increasingly complex schemes. However, even the best laid plans often go awry, and your most recent plan has fallen apart and left you stranded, in of all places, San Diego! While the Prince is planning an attack on the very people you've been running from! He's made it clear that your ability to stay in the city long enough to devise a new plan is contingent on you helping out with the war effort. You will, but you can't wait to be on the next plane, train or cargo van to somewhere else far away."
